    <item>
      <title>经济数据推高利率，比特币跌破 10 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/bitcoin-slumps-below-100-000-as-eco-data-pushes-rates-higher</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币重返 10 万美元上方的势头并未持续太久。周二，随着新经济数据公布，美国国债收益率飙升，比特币跟随美国股市下跌，创下两周多以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/bitcoin-slumps-below-100-000-as-eco-data-pushes-rates-higher</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 19:42:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
